nvest opportunistically in transformational change focused on companies effecting disruptive innovation and those undergoing positive change as the result of a dynamic catalyst integrated research approach fundamental bottomup analysis portfolio managers analysts and traders work together without compartmentalization copyright  gardner lewis asset management all rights reserved  wilmingtonwest chester pike chadds ford pa  designed by eisenman associates home   directions   contact   legal our history  gardner lewis gardner lewis about our history investment philosophy research investment strategies alternative strategies traditional strategies venture capital and real assets contact our history ‘’ centreville de gardner lewis asset management was founded in april  by w whitfield gardner and john l lewis iv the firm is rooted in the belief that a “rollupthesleeves” approach to investing is the best way to uncover unrecognized opportunities since its inception the firm has been privatelyowned and maintains independence from any outside business affiliations or joint ventures while client growth and research team depth necessitated a larger working space gardner lewis remains rooted in the brandywine valley with its office located in chadds ford pennsylvania ‘’ chadds ford pa our firm fosters a team environment to provide the highest level of operational expertise and service to our clients  from the beginning gardner lewis has valued a distinctive firm culture and has focused on capturing the highest returns through a process that is differentiated and consistent  we believe these factors are integral to the value we offer our clients w whitfield gardner portfolio manager  partner mr gardner has served as chairman and chief executive officer of gardner lewis asset management since the firm’s founding in  previously he was a lead portfolio manager with friess associates and its brandywine fund prior to joining friess associates he worked as an investment analyst with investments orange nassau a netherlandsbased venture capital firm with interests in both private and public companies this position stemmed from employment with mbank then a  billion bank holding company where he analyzed companies as well as industry groups he began his investment career at lehman brothers kuhn loeb prior to the shearson merger mr gardner received his bba in finance from southern methodist university bernard j diggins portfolio managerpartner mr diggins has been with the firm since  and oversees research prior to joining gardner lewis mr diggins was in the corporate and securities group of drinker biddle  reath specializing in mergers and acquisitions and venture capital finance mr diggins received his ba from the ohio state university and was awarded his jd magna cum laude from the dickinson school of law at pennsylvania state university about copyright  gardner lewis asset management all rights reserved  wilmingtonwest chester pike chadds ford pa  designed by eisenman associates home   directions   contact   legal gardner lewis asset management lp  chadds ford  pa  company information products resources my account talk to a db advisor  business directory pa chadds ford investment advice investment advisory service gardner lewis asset management lp g gardner lewis asset management lp claim this business  wlmgtn w chester park chadds ford pa  get directions   wwwgardnerlewiscom business info founded  incorporated annual revenue  employee count  industries investment advisory service contacts william gardner contact business your email address subject message send message company summary since  the company has been providing investment advisory service verified status unverified address unverified last verified  phone unverified payment method unverified view full report similar businesses nearby our similar businesses nearby shows similar businesses in their industry and region based on information found in their dun  bradstreet credibility review p